8 December 2013The briefing to be held by Minister in The Presidency, Collins Chabane on developments relating to the state funeral of President Nelson Mandela is postponed to a later time today in light of the church services that are currently underway as part of the national day of prayer and reflection.The details are as follows: Date: Sunday, 8 December 2013 Time: 15h00 Venue: SABC Studios, AucklandEnquiries: Phumla Williams Cell: 083 5010 139Issued by Government Communication and Information System (GCIS)